propDescriptions.ampmInClock: Display ampm controls under the clock (instead of in the toolbar).
propDescriptions.autoFocus: Set to true if focus should be moved to clock picker.
propDescriptions.classes: Sobrescreve ou extende os estilos aplicados para o componente. Veja a API CSS abaixo para maiores detalhes.
propDescriptions.components: The components used for each slot. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propDescriptions.componentsProps: The props used for each slot inside.
propDescriptions.disableIgnoringDatePartForTimeValidation: Do not ignore date part when validating min/max time.
propDescriptions.getClockLabelText: Accessible text that helps user to understand which time and view is selected.
propDescriptions.getHoursClockNumberText: Get clock number aria-text for hours.
propDescriptions.getMinutesClockNumberText: Get clock number aria-text for minutes.
propDescriptions.getSecondsClockNumberText: Get clock number aria-text for seconds.
propDescriptions.maxTime: Max time acceptable time. For input validation date part of passed object will be ignored if disableIgnoringDatePartForTimeValidation not specified.
propDescriptions.minTime: Min time acceptable time. For input validation date part of passed object will be ignored if disableIgnoringDatePartForTimeValidation not specified.
propDescriptions.shouldDisableTime: Dynamically check if time is disabled or not. If returns false appropriate time point will ot be acceptable.
